.DT
query_features_in_region
Disk World creator help
query_features_in_region

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_features_in_region -  This method finds all the features inside the specified region.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * query_features_in_region(int x1_orig,
int y1_orig,
int x2_orig,
int y2_orig)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^x1%^RESET%^ - the top x location
%^BOLD%^y1%^RESET%^ - the top y location
%^BOLD%^x2%^RESET%^ - the bottom x location
%^BOLD%^y2%^RESET%^ - the bottom y location
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the features in the region
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/world_map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method finds all the features inside the specified region.  This
is quite expensive in terms of evaluation cost, so do not try and call
this too much.  Cache the results if possible.
.EP

